    <item>
      <title>Installation: Introduction</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/theme/introduction/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/theme/introduction/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#39;version-management&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;Version management&lt;a href=&#39;#version-management&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#39;assets-used-in-the-theme&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-2&#34;&gt;Assets used in the theme&lt;a href=&#39;#assets-used-in-the-theme&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Asset&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Minimum version&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;Hugo (Extended version)&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;sc-parameter&#34;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases/tag/v0.156.0&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;0.156.0&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://bulma.io/&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;Bulma&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;sc-parameter&#34;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://github.com/jgthms/bulma/releases/tag/1.0.4&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;1.0.4&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;notification is-info&#34;&gt;Several other assets are used in Shadocs. Versions can be found within the &lt;em&gt;.bmycconfig.json&lt;/em&gt; file and assets are automatically updated using the &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://github.com/jgazeau/bmyc#bump-me-if-you-can-bmyc&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;Bmyc&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&#xA; library.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#39;installation&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;Installation&lt;a href=&#39;#installation&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#39;hugo-website-creation&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-2&#34;&gt;Hugo website creation&lt;a href=&#39;#hugo-website-creation&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;To create a Hugo website, the Hugo documentation provides a complete &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/getting-started/quick-start/&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;Quickstart&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&#xA; which includes all the necessary steps to easily and quickly create a Hugo website.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Installation: Configuration</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/theme/configuration/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/theme/configuration/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#39;general-considerations&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;General considerations&lt;a href=&#39;#general-considerations&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To configure a Hugo website using the theme, there are three types of configuration:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Type&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Configuration file&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/getting-started/configuration/&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;Standard Hugo configuration&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;./hugo.toml&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Specific configuration using &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/variables/site/&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;site variables&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;./hugo.toml&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Default theme configuration&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;.themes/shadocs/data/themeParams.toml&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#39;specific-configuration&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;Specific configuration&lt;a href=&#39;#specific-configuration&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sc-snippet-wrapper is-flex is-flex-wrap-wrap my-4&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;sc-snippet-container&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;sc-snippet&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;sc-snippet-caption&#34;&gt;hugo.toml ([params] section)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-toml&#34; data-lang=&#34;toml&#34;&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#39;default-theme-configuration&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;Default theme configuration&lt;a href=&#39;#default-theme-configuration&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sc-snippet-wrapper is-flex is-flex-wrap-wrap my-4&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;sc-snippet-container&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;sc-snippet&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;sc-snippet-caption&#34;&gt;themeParams.toml&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-toml&#34; data-lang=&#34;toml&#34;&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Installation: Extend the theme</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/theme/extend/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/theme/extend/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#39;general-considerations&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;General considerations&lt;a href=&#39;#general-considerations&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;As every other Hugo theme, Shadocs theme can be extended and modified for specific purposes.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;notification is-info&#34;&gt;For more information, check &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/templates/&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;Hugo template documentation&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#39;html-customization&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;HTML customization&lt;a href=&#39;#html-customization&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Several custom HTML layout files are available in the theme.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;These files are empty by default, but they can be defined within a specific website (using the &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/templates/lookup-order/&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;Hugo&amp;rsquo;s Lookup Order&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&#xA;), to include specific code at a specific place, directly within the global HTML layout, without having to modify the default theme layout.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
