      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/theme/contribute/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#39;find-a-bug&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;Find a bug?&lt;a href=&#39;#find-a-bug&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you find any bug within the theme, don&amp;rsquo;t hesitate to &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;https://github.com/jgazeau/shadocs/issues/new&#34;&#xA;    class=&#34;is-pretty-link&#34;&gt;raise and report a new issue&lt;/a&#xA;&gt;&#xA;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#39;want-to-contribute&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;Want to contribute?&lt;a href=&#39;#want-to-contribute&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you want to contribute directly to the project, don&amp;rsquo;t hesitate do fork the project and raise a Pull Request to submit your modifications. All ideas are welcome and I&amp;rsquo;ll be glad to check them.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#39;want-to-run-the-documentation-website-locally&#39; class=&#34;title is-flex is-align-items-center mt-4 is-1&#34;&gt;Want to run the documentation website locally?&lt;a href=&#39;#want-to-run-the-documentation-website-locally&#39; class=&#39;anchor&#39;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To run the current website locally, run the following command:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
